{{ZScriptNote}}

{{c|SectorTagIterator}} is a class that can find {{struct|Sector|sectors}} of a map.

==Usage==
{{c|SectorTagIterator}} is not instantiated directly, but instead by calling [[Structs:LevelLocals#Dynamic|{{c|Level.CreateSectorTagIterator}}]].

==Methods==
===Static===
*{{c|SectorTagIterator '''Create'''(int ''tag'', line ''defline'' }}={{c| null)}} {{deprecated}}
:Deprecated method for creating a SectorTagIterator (was valid before GZDoom 3.8). Use [[Structs:LevelLocals#Dynamic|{{c|Level.CreateSectorTagIterator}}]] instead.
===Non-static===
*{{c|int '''Next'''()}}
:Returns an index of the next sector in the linked list of sectors.
*{{c|int '''NextCompat'''(bool ''compat'', int ''secnum'')}}
:{{moreinfo}}

